text: Kendall Phillips (born December 28, 1991) is an American country singer- songwriter, and actress. She is most recently known for being a 2010 and 2011 National Finalist in the Colgate Country Showdown and for being a contestant on the 2006 season of American Idol.Guyett,Susan.
